did.unittitle: Headstone of John Andrew Cook, a boyfriend of Brezing when they were teenagers and who died under mysterious circumstances; "Farewell John Andrew, son of P & Barbra Cook Born in Nashville, Tenn. Aug. 24, 1859; Died Sept. 22, 1875 Aged 15 Yrs. and 1 Mo."
